ev\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3764}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 6-foot-11 forward made his official NBA debut with the Philadelphia 76ers, the team that drafted him in the second round in 2021, before being dealt to the Los Angeles Clippers as part of a trade that was centered around James Harden.\\u00c2 Fun fact \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Petrusev is one of six former Gonzaga players to win a gold medal in an international tournament (FIBA or Olympics).\\u00c2 Players who haven\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t officially been named to a roster: BRANDON CLARKE, CANADA Team Canada has yet to officially release its training camp roster, though it would appear Clarke is due an invite after he committed to a three-year agreement with the national team in 2022.\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 4572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4086, \"end\": 4106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Clippers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.119951869621234e-104, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Clippers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Clippers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Clippers\"}, {\"begin\": 4151, \"end\": 4156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3333248922789777e-32, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 4210, \"end\": 4217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonzaga_Bulldogs_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.10230763876924e-54, \"text\": \"Gonzaga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonzaga_Bulldogs_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonzaga_Bulldogs_men's_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 4357, \"end\": 4371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc